            <h3>CRITICAL EXAM-DAY TIPS:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>✓ Mnemonic for Acts &amp; Years:</strong> Wild-72, Water-74, Forest-80, Air-81, EP-86, PLI-91, NGT-10. Practice this — comes up every time.</li>
