                <li><strong>✓ India ratification dates:</strong> CBD 1994, UNFCCC 1993, Basel 1992, Kyoto 2002, Paris 2016, Kigali 2021, Minamata 2018.</li>
                <li><strong>✓ NEP 2006:</strong> only POLICY (not law); doesn't have legal teeth.</li>
